<br>
With much effort and will the half drowned dark elf dragged his body onto the sanded shore and lay there for several minutes panting as if he were a dog.  He rolled onto his back, looked to the sky and sighed.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Antonica, how I missed your lands...&quot; he muttered between breaths.  <br>
<br>
Lifting himself slowly he started his long travel to his homeland to which he hadn't visited in months upon months.  New scars, memories of old friends dead, new skills and old pains rippled throughout Malignus' body.  Nothing seemed familiar here.  The desert was unusually lonely and the sands didn't whip around like shards of glass.  Clearing the last dune and entering into the cave leading to the commons he noticed a strange absence in....a presence.  Almost not a single traveller could be seen galloping through one of the liveliest trading spots in all of Norrath, atleast that's how it was before he had left.  <br>
<br>
&quot;These new lands bring abandon to our ancient ones.&quot; Malignus whispered under his breath.  Clearing the entrance of the cave and galloping onto fresh grass and trees he made a sprint to the edge of the mountains and into Nektulos.  It didn't take long before a rumbling began to follow him.  Quickening his pace he ignored all that was around him until the rumbling slowly faded like the wind and he was once again in friendly grounds.  The dark abandon of Nektulos forest.     <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.showMessage?topicID=347.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.showMessage?topicID=553.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=543.topic&index=3><img src=http://turkkurt.homestead.com/files/z/Sasi/brmreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.threadControl?topicID=543.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=543.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/fthemissednotethetavern.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=543.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub76.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option va